data.description:
Améliore l'ergonomie des forums "mobile" sur PC.
À utiliser avec l'extension "Redirector" https://addons.mozilla.org/fr/firefox/addon/redirector/
Et cette redirection :
Include pattern: https://www.jeuxvideo.com/forums/*
Redirect to: https://m.jeuxvideo.com/forums/$1

data.name: DLsite Tomorrow
Google Podcasts - Dark Theme
data.description:
Dark Theme!
It can also automatically change based on if Dark Mode is enabled on your Operating System.

e.g: Light mode MacOS will display the website in its original white format, but if you toggle Dark Mode on, it'll automatically switch to the dark theme.

You can help and contribute via GitHub: https://github.com/RolandUdv/Google-Podcasts---Dark-Theme
